Pros: Great location as it is walking distance from shops and restaurants and across the street from a nice sandy beach. The pool is clean and the grounds of the complex well maintained. The condo is clean and has everything you will need for your stay.
Cons: The view is obstructed by the shopping center in front of the condo. There is a loading zone for the shops close by, so it may be noisy in the morning for the person sleeping in the living room; 
NB! the pool area is a "quiet zone", so it is great for swimming, but if you are with small kids, you have to keep the noise down and cannot play with a ball

